Leads & Trial Memberships

Lead & Trial Memberships

What is Lead & Trial Maximizer?

Trial Maximizer shows you a list of all your prospects and trials. It provides all the information you need to follow-up on your trial memberships and new prospects.

Trial Phases

Trial Phases are the steps a prospect will go through to become a paying member. You can create your own phases to make Leads & Trials Maximizer unique to your business. Click here to customize the Trial Phases.
